&lt;h1 id="science-expands-our-vision-of-reality"&gt;Science Expands Our Vision of Reality&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apr 28 2021&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The multiverse is another step in this direction&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Many scientists and philosophers have talked about the concept of a &lt;strong&gt;multiverse&lt;/strong&gt;. But we&amp;rsquo;re talking about a very strict, very sober understanding of what a multiverse is.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Every Theory Is Held Inside a Physical Substrate</title><link>https://linguista.cn/naval/orig/every-theory-is-held-inside-a-physical-substrate/</link><pubDate>Mon, 12 Apr 2021 18:06:51 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/naval/orig/every-theory-is-held-inside-a-physical-substrate/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/naval/zh/every-theory-is-held-inside-a-physical-substrate.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
